                        alert(`Demo Mode: Showing sample data for tracking ID: ${repair.trackingId}\n\nIn production, this would show real repair status from our database.\n\nTry these demo IDs:\n- TR-DEMO123 (In Progress)\n- TR-DEMO456 (Completed)`);
